channel.title: How to change cache folder name whose will works?
channel.description: i got xenon cache, i wanna rename it to my own name, if i rename it, client says: Unabble downloading cache. What exactly i have to do? Please help.

item.title: How to change cache folder name whose will works?
item.dc:creator: @RandQm RandQm
item.description:
@RandQm wrote:

Deptas1599:

my cache XENON, founded 1265 items, what exactly file i must rename (+ cache)?

open the file signlink.java
inside the file search for "findcachedir"
you will see the current name somewhere in there, change it to xenon

item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Literally search the name of the cache in your Client’s source folder.
Open whatever files come up, and rename the cache.

Compile, and magic. It’s changed.
